data.description:
EXCLUSIVE OPPORTUNITY! This property is an extraordinary find, boasting a delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch-style home with an open concept and a split floor plan, situated on over 13 acres of land. Included are solar panels valued at over $50k, provided at no extra cost. Whether you aspire to operate a small farm or create a serene family haven outside of town within an excellent school district, this property is tailored to meet your needs.

The residence features a 32x24 spray foam insulated shop with a sink, water heater, and electric, offering the potential for conversion into a secondary living space. Additional amenities comprise a 61x65 horse barn with 5 stalls, pole barns, loafing sheds, a yard tool shed, $45k in smooth fencing, RV hookup with cleanout, a caliche-bottomed stock pond with a 12x16 pier, a gated entrance, and much more. Noteworthy is the provision of a dog shelter with electric, ready for the installation of an air conditioner. No compromises have been made in ensuring the quality and completeness of this property.
